              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27926974/" class="">第168页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3312360/" class=" " title="巫仙">巫仙</a>
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="27926974">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">德若水之源，才若水之波；德若木之根，才若木之枝。德而无才，则近于愚人；才而无德，则近于小人。两者不可兼时，与其无德而近于小人，毋宁无才而近于愚人。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-08-04 14:22</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                德若水之源，才若水之波；德若木之根，才若木之枝。德而无才，则近于愚人；才而无德，则近于小人。两者不可兼时，与其无德而近于小人，毋宁无才而近于愚人。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
